his corner kick sailed over the penalty box and was played back to 
the middle, where Bravo headed it past MetroStars (4-5) goalkeeper 
Mike Ammann. 
</P>
<P>
	Colorado has not lost a game in regulation this season, while  
the MetroStars continued to struggle on offense. New York-New 
Jersey has scored just eight goals this season -- three coming last 
Saturday against last-place Miami. 
